    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You haven't said which version you want, but an archive of the JDK 8 source code can be <a href=\"http://download.java.net/openjdk/jdk8/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">downloaded here</a>, along with <a href=\"http://download.java.net/openjdk/jdk7/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">JDK 7</a> and <a href=\"http://download.java.net/openjdk/jdk6/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">JDK 6</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Additionally you can browse or clone the Mercurial repositories: <a href=\"http://hg.openjdk.java.net/jdk8/jdk8/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">8</a>, <a href=\"http://hg.openjdk.java.net/jdk7/jdk7/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">7</a>, <a href=\"http://hg.openjdk.java.net/jdk6/jdk6/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">6</a>.</p>\n"
  }, {
