    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This file is contained in the <a href=\"http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/widget/jdk6.jsp\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">standard JDK download</a>. Also your Linux system probably has the JDK in the repository. In my Ubuntu Linux, the file is located in <em>/usr/lib/jvm/java-6-sun-1.6.0.20/src.zip</em>.</p>\n"
