    "question_id" : 2896727,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I had this problem with my Ubuntu.</p>\n<p>All I needed to do to get sources for my Java installation was:</p>\n<pre><code>sudo apt-get install sun-java6-source\n</code></pre>\n"
